OL,3,CMan accused of #595,000 romance fraud
OL,5,FA man has appeared in court accused of
OL,6,Fromance fraud against six women
OL,7,Famounting to almost #600,000
OL,9,FMarc Cole-Jones, 52, has been accused
OL,10,Fof 22 counts of fraud by false
OL,11,Frepresentation totalling #595,791.
OL,13,FCole-Jones, from Church Grove,
OL,14,FDonnington, Telford, was charged with
OL,15,Foffences in August 2025.
OL,17,FHe appeared at Chester Crown Court on
OL,18,FWednesday 24 September for a brief pre-
OL,19,Ftrial hearing.
