OL,3,CMan accused of #595,000 romance fraud
OL,5,FCole-Jones, who is also known as Marc
OL,6,FCole, Marcus Cole-Jones, and Marc
OL,7,FSands, did not enter any pleas.
OL,9,FThe six women were allegedly defrauded
OL,10,Fbetween 2009 and 2024 and are from
OL,11,FCheshire, Lancashire, Manchester,
OL,12,FShropshire, Warwickshire, and the West
OL,13,FMidlands.
OL,15,FJudge Natalie Cuddy bailed Cole-Jones
OL,16,Funtil 5 February 2026, when he must
OL,17,Fappear back at the same court for a
OL,18,Fplea and trial preparation hearing.
OL,20,FA trial date is yet to be fixed.
