OL,5,FCole-Jones' bail conditions are that
OL,6,Fhe must provide police details of his
OL,7,Fbank accounts and mobile phone use,
OL,8,Freport to Telford police station each
OL,9,Fweek and is not to contact any of the
OL,10,Fsix complainanats.
OL,12,FThe charges follow an investigation by
OL,13,Fdetectives from the Economic Crime
OL,14,FUnit at Cheshire Police.
